\f1\b0\fs40 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}Salt\
{\listtext	\'95	}3 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil, divided\
{\listtext	\'95	}5 slices center cut bacon, chopped\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 medium {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/onion/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 onion}}, chopped\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 to 3 grated garlic cloves\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/bay-leaf/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 bay leaf}}\
